⦿ .spun — the five-fold spin of The Erdtree
node ER · ER · ⟦The Erdtree:ER:c1f0a6⟧

WHO   — The Erdtree — the golden tree at the center of the world
WHAT  — The colossal tree of gold that dominates the Lands Between, visible from everywhere.
WHERE — ER · Elden Ring  Framework inputs: the frame  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
WHY   — It is the world's axis — faith, law, and landmark in one — the refined form of the primordial Crucible and Marika's prison.
HOW   — Seat of the Golden Order and home of the Elden Ring; its blessing is grace, and its leaves are said to return the dead to its roots in cycles of burial.

awareness — what the node knows of itself:
  The axis of the world stands golden and sealed, and will not open until it burns.

